umbers/Nash Information Services|url=http://www.the-numbers.com/market/Distributors2008.php|year=2009|accessdate=2010-01-19}} [http://www.boxofficemojo.com/studio/?view=company&view2=yearly&yr=2007&p=.htm Studio Market Share (2007)], [http://www.boxofficemojo.com/studio/?view=company&view2=yearly&yr=2006&p=.htm Studio Market Share (2006)], [http://www.boxofficemojo.com/studio/?view=company&view2=yearly&yr=2005&p=.htm Studio Market Share (2005)], and [http://www.boxofficemojo.com/studio/?view=company&view2=yearly&yr=2004&p=.htm Studio Market Share (2004)]. Retrieved March 3, 2009.</ref>
