'''Shadow Fighter''' hangul]]:섀도우 파이터, ''Shaedou Paiteo'') is a [[Korea]]n [[animation]]. It is a product of the major anime broadcaster [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation]], and the [[3-D film|3D]] animation was done by [[Yellow Film]]. The story centers on the fighter character, a war and robot fight squirrel.
